  <md:title>Deviance and Control</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you should be able to:</para><list id="list-00001">
<item>Define deviance, and explain the nature of deviant behavior</item>
<item>Differentiate between methods of social control</item>
