<section id="fs-id1345457" class="further-research" type="further-research">
        <title>Further Research</title>
        <para id="import-auto-id2195439">Although we rarely think of it in this way, deviance can have a positive effect on society. Check out the <link url="https://openstax.org/l/Positive_Deviance" window="new">Positive Deviance Initiative</link>, a program initiated by Tufts University to promote social movements around the world that strive to improve people’s lives.</para>
